metadata.title: The Bering Sea - Alaska Geographic
metadata.description:
A look at the environment, interaction of species and human dependence on those species, as well as what can be done to protect and preserve one of the world's
richest ecosystems. With index. Bering Sea Vol. 26, No. 3.
metadata.notes:
Purpose: A book about the Bering Sea related to whales, mammals, seabirds, fish, seals and traditional knowledge
